channel.title: Help Me Please, just joined Cant log in
channel.description:
Okay...I used to play modscape alot back then evem before the download, And iv'e been bored latley so i downloaded the game and registerd! I run the game, Type my user: Dressdel And my password: ************** And i type in a ID like 66.36.243.100 And it says No respone from login server please wait another minute. And it keep says.
I registerd to the site and i need help. What servers? How do i log into one? How do i command for items? Etc Etc Etc I'm a newbie now. Please give help and tell! please Or does this game evn work still? :(

item.title: Help Me Please, just joined Cant log in
item.dc:creator: @durial12 durial12
item.description:
@durial12 wrote:

Servers can register on the server status page: http://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php

Simply look on the list and choose a server! (Some may require you to download a custom client designed for their server and all their pointless custom items.)

You do not have to use a set password, in fact you can use any username as well. This site and the servers are not joined in any way like that.
